Muchidzidzo [[Taranyika]], '''chivhuramabwe'' (Hailstorm) zvinoreva mvura inoturuka iri tuma[[godo]] twemvura yakabundira nechando kuita tumatombo. Tumatombo utwu tunoti kana tuchinge twasvika pasi twotanga kunyungudika nokuda kwe[[hujoto]] hwakakwira pasi pacho. Mvura inonyungudika noku[[gwamba]] pahujoto 0<sup>o</sup>C.


Mune dzimwe nzvimbo chivhuramabwe chinoparadza zvirimwa chichiparura mashizha ezvirimwa zvikurusei zvirimwa zvine mashizha makuru sechibage nefodya.
